{
  "stem": "6257.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember it being mentioned, some money came from-- through them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there's another some sort of [? health ?] organization just called [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tolls ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's-- I don't know how that worked-- how they worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they had-- they seemed busy, yes, with the kitchen, which she organized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know what else she was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because some of it was connected to the underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, yes, there was-- you could tell a lot of agitation, people meeting in those courtyards, and talking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there were placards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which, I don't remember exactly what they said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they must have said there was this new order, that a lot of Jews would have to be sent away from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And always, only some would be allowed to stay if they had some special jobs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yes, some people became very frightened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then-- so-- and my mother had some documents at first for herself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because she was-- I don't know connect-- I suppose they had some through the-- I know the Polish name is [POLISH] but probably Judenrat organization, I seem to remember, for herself.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And me and my sister was-- I remember the first time the Germans and Ukrainians came to collect people who-- who had no documents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember me slaying this piece of paper and being terribly frightened, and finding in the last minute and showing it to them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they went way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But very soon afterwards, we sort of realized, we were told that the documents, they would not be enough.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at first we were given some sort of watches by my uncle to try to bribe the Ukrainians and Germans when they come, so that they shouldn't take us away.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
